Class MakelangeloRobotSettings

java.lang.Object
com.marginallyclever.makelangeloRobot.settings.MakelangeloRobotSettings
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public final class MakelangeloRobotSettings
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
All the hardware settings for a single plotter robot. Does not store state information.
Author:
Dan Royer TODO move tool names into translations and add a color palette system for quantizing colors.
